## Tunables ‚Äî single source of truth

### Wave scaling (`js/hunt/hunt-stage.js` + `js/hunt/hunt-waves.js`)

| Constant            | Value | Module            | Effect                                                          |
| ------------------- | ----- | ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `WAVE_COUNT_EARLY`  | 5     | hunt-stage.js     | Stages 1‚Äì6 wave count                                           |
| `WAVE_COUNT_MID`    | 10    | hunt-stage.js     | Stages 7‚Äì12 wave count                                          |
| `WAVE_COUNT_LATE`   | 15    | hunt-stage.js     | Stages 13‚Äì18 wave count                                         |
| `WAVE_SEC_EARLY`    | 90    | hunt-stage.js     | Per-wave duration (s), early tier                               |
| `WAVE_SEC_MID`      | 100   | hunt-stage.js     | Per-wave duration (s), mid tier                                 |
| `WAVE_SEC_LATE`     | 110   | hunt-stage.js     | Per-wave duration (s), late tier                                |
| `WAVE_RATE_MUL`     | 1.5   | hunt-waves.js     | Spawn-rate multiplier compounded each wave                      |
| `WAVE_STAT_BASE`    | 0.18  | hunt-waves.js     | STAT_MUL = 1 + (waveIndex0 √ó WAVE_STAT_BASE), applied to hp/dmg |
| `WAVE_BASE_RATE_MIN`| 0.5   | hunt-waves.js     | Within-wave start spawn rate (enemies/s)                        |
| `WAVE_BASE_RATE_MAX`| 1.5   | hunt-waves.js     | Within-wave end spawn rate (enemies/s)                          |
| `NIGHT_SPAWN_MUL`   | 1.6   | hunt-waves.js     | Night-mode spawn-rate multiplier                                |
| `NIGHT_STAT_MUL`    | 1.4   | hunt-waves.js     | Night-mode hp/dmg multiplier                                    |

Wave 1 (waveIndex0 = 0) ‚Üí 1.0√ó spawn rate, 1.0√ó stats ‚Äî approachable per
architect mandate. Wave 5 ‚Üí 5.06√ó spawn, 1.72√ó stats. Wave 15 ‚Üí 291√ó spawn
rate (capped naturally by within-wave ramp ceiling), 3.52√ó stats. Boss spawns
at start of the final wave so it shares the chaos rather than dropping into
an empty arena.

Stage `durationSec` now equals `waveCount √ó waveDurationSec`:
- Tier 1 (5 √ó 90s)  = 450s = 7.5 min per stage
- Tier 2 (10 √ó 100s) = 1000s = 16.7 min per stage
- Tier 3 (15 √ó 110s) = 1650s = 27.5 min per stage

### Buff system (`js/meta/meta-buffs.js`)

| Buff ID          | Kind     | Default duration | Hooked at                                                                    |
| ---------------- | -------- | ---------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `damage_x2`      | duration | 60 000 ms        | `hunt-player.baseDamage` ‚Äî multiplies output damage √ó2                        |
| `wood_x2`        | duration | 90 000 ms        | `hunt-player.autoAttack` stump-chop ‚Äî drops a second wood + a second coin    |
| `instant_turret` | oneshot  | n/a              | `hunt-player.constructionTick` ‚Äî turret slot auto-completes, buff consumed   |
| `revive`         | oneshot  | n/a              | `hunt-player.takeDamage` ‚Äî at hp ‚â§ 0 restores maxHp, no `player:died` emit   |

Activation paths:
1. Level-select panel ‚Äî 4 gold-bordered buttons ‚Üí `WG.Ads.showRewardedVideo()`
   ‚Üí `WG.Buffs.activate(id, ms)` + gold screen flash + cha_ching audio (via
   reused `iap:purchase` event in EVENT_MAP).
2. Death modal ‚Äî `Watch Ad to Revive` button (heartbeat-pulse animation +
   5s dramatic countdown) ‚Üí ad ‚Üí restore HP, increment
   `runtime.reviveCount`. Limit 1 per stage run (`REVIVE_LIMIT_PER_RUN`).

### Death-modal revive (`js/hunt/hunt-results.js`)

| Constant                 | Value | Effect                                            |
| ------------------------ | ----- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| `REVIVE_COUNTDOWN_SEC`   | 5     | Dramatic window before stage truly ends           |
| `REVIVE_LIMIT_PER_RUN`   | 1     | Max ad-revives per stage run                      |

CSS animation `@keyframes hr-heartbeat` injects on first death modal: 0.9s
infinite scale 1 ‚Üí 1.06 + box-shadow ripple in red. Visible in stage 1 fail.

