## Architect mandate compliance

- Difficulty curve: wave 1 baseline (1.0√ó / 1.0√ó); late waves brutal but
  predictable from compounding constants ‚Äî not random-feeling.
- Ad-buff buttons visually distinct: gold border, gold ‚ñ∫ AD pill, scale-bounce
  on tap (0.94√ó). "ON" pill swaps in when buff active.
- Revive modal: heartbeat-pulse (CSS keyframes), 5s countdown, dramatic
  red-on-black panel above the stats row.
- Buff activation: cha_ching audio (via `iap:purchase` emit hitting existing
  EVENT_MAP row), full-screen gold flash (`flashScreen`), persistent HUD
  badge `2√ó DMG 60s` drawn top-right of the canvas HUD.

